{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1324186, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "要不是这个洞我还不知道原来一楼的热水会有不同 那你告诉我高楼层生活用的热水从哪打 而且你管热水叫权益 这真的不应该是基本的生活保障吗", "timestamp": 1616587168, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324196, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不是针对你 但学校打一棒子再给个甜枣 你就只记得甜枣而不考虑你该不该挨这一棒子吗", "timestamp": 1616587239, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324201, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你疑似有点魔怔了\n", "timestamp": 1616587301, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324208, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "总觉得酸奶冻讲话味好重啊 就是那种搞了很多年学生工作的人的说话方式", "timestamp": 1616587364, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324220, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 是因为北京市政府的规定 不赖清华 sigh", "timestamp": 1616587427, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324221, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 不好意思 没有学工经历", "timestamp": 1616587442, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324237, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "反对直饮水洗脚，我自己是去浴室接热水，但是挺不方便的。\n希望可以在洗漱间接个热水龙头，接洗浴间的热水管，供洗脚用。", "timestamp": 1616587513, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324245, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 哎 跟电动车一样吧 没有上面兴风作浪 学校维持现状何乐而不为呢 小桥报刊亭拆了就是sb中的sb 低端人口这次也不是秋宝提的 无解。", "timestamp": 1616587615, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324248, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同意bob", "timestamp": 1616587639, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324266, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不在乎那点钱，非要去接直饮水洗脚虽然可以理解，但是不是什么值得倡导的行为啊。", "timestamp": 1616587718, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324281, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 如果有两台机器的话 举手之劳何乐而不为 尤其是在未知情的情况下。\n不过算了，儿孙自有儿孙福。反正我走了，下一次取消直饮水的时候，也不用care了。", "timestamp": 1616587822, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324297, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 直饮水有复杂的检测要求，一台直饮水机一年的检测费就16万元，还有排污费。。。清华这么多直饮水机。。。可是对应之经费能用在水上的没多少（不属于基建）。当时学校和北京市能让步实属不易。没想到啊。。。", "timestamp": 1616587936, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324299, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 北京市规定高层不许有热水？", "timestamp": 1616587947, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324315, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 规定一台直饮水机一年要缴纳16万的检测经费。每个月检测一次。学校拿不出这个钱。此外清华排污超标，环保局也不让。", "timestamp": 1616588078, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324324, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我是说，高层为什么不可以有热水", "timestamp": 1616588128, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324326, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 没说直饮水机", "timestamp": 1616588143, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324331, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "据我所知很多学校都是独立卫浴吧，我们没有独立卫浴连洗脚水都不给吗", "timestamp": 1616588179, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324335, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 哪个高层没有热水呀 sigh", "timestamp": 1616588221, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324350, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 有的就是你说的直饮水", "timestamp": 1616588347, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324356, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没有其他热水", "timestamp": 1616588360, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324395, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 那也挺好 没有就用呗", "timestamp": 1616588758, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324492, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不好意思，没觉得学校给你提供直饮水是基本的生活保障。在家养尊处优什么都有就算了，出门没人惯着你，像直饮水这些配套不是你应得的，而是额外的。", "timestamp": 1616589714, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324527, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 不提供直饮水 可 请允许自己烧水", "timestamp": 1616589945, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1324955, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 抱歉我可能是好日子过惯了平时生活水平太高了没体验过G君所经历过的水深火热的生活祝您身体健康", "timestamp": 1616593490, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325492, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 宿舍可以自己烧水的啊。。。", "timestamp": 1616597557, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325525, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: ？？？", "timestamp": 1616597776, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325527, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是违禁电器啊", "timestamp": 1616597789, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325676, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "宿舍烧水是绝对不可以的啊", "timestamp": 1616598910, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325906, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: @北京消防", "timestamp": 1616600256, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326306, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你多少沾点😅", "timestamp": 1616602530, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326823, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 并不是，符合3c且低于1000W的是可以使用的，你到底听谁说的啊", "timestamp": 1616606699, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326824, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 违禁你个大头鬼", "timestamp": 1616606712, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326841, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: ……天告诉你的", "timestamp": 1616606842, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326857, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不明白 每天都有热水洗澡，怎么就没有热水洗脚了？", "timestamp": 1616607054, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326862, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不可以的哦(´-ω-`)加热的都不能", "timestamp": 1616607109, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326872, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 可以的，不信现在62783333咨询公寓管理中心。", "timestamp": 1616607246, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326882, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我说婷婷，有没有直饮水不是学校的事吗？咋就是你争取的了...?", "timestamp": 1616607385, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326883, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 宿舍不可以烧水，烹饪相关的都不行，你是不是学生啊", "timestamp": 1616607387, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326887, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有断电保护装置，功率低于1000W的，符合3C认证的电烧水壶，随便用。\n另外 建议学校之间把直饮水 直接都改成加热水 \n省事，不用吃力不讨好", "timestamp": 1616607421, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326894, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Nathan: 麻烦确认后再出来喷。", "timestamp": 1616607464, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326916, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Margaret: #58019", "timestamp": 1616607810, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326922, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Margaret: 不好意思，不是呢，换饮水机的时候我当时在xx交换，我回来后一直争取给北京市一直反馈，学校开座谈会就换回来了。那之前清华大家度过了两三个月没有直饮水的生活。大概就是热水一股沙子味儿？", "timestamp": 1616607968, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326923, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/xssqglfwzx/info/1009/1006.htm卧槽看了下好像真的没有明说禁烧水 但是开学的时候各种安全教育确实说过不让烧水的", "timestamp": 1616607994, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326933, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: #260968", "timestamp": 1616608151, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326937, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 楼长安全检查的时候我还在烧热水，无事发生。只能烧水的水壶是可以的，可以用来烹饪的不行", "timestamp": 1616608196, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326939, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 并没有的。摸摸。", "timestamp": 1616608214, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1327003, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 挺好的，赞", "timestamp": 1616609237, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1327272, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Paul", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "原来可以烧水吗！那为什么不让用电饭锅呀，我看淘宝上有那种300-600W带3C认证的小电饭锅，垂涎很久了没敢买呜呜", "timestamp": 1616631464, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328415, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Paul: 所以这是“宿舍神器”，偶尔煮面啥的就跟很多人电动车充电一样常见，但是做饭肯定就……", "timestamp": 1616643556, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1329894, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Queen", "pid": 260518, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "啊？紫荆公寓还有一段时间曾经没有直饮水？？怎么我印象里一直是有热水的？", "timestamp": 1616658785, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 21, "pid": 260518, "reply": 50, "tag": null, "text": "#260425\n#酸奶冻#\n忽然有点后悔为大家争取来直饮水的权利了。\n认真。\n2019年8月，全校所有楼宇统一废除直饮水。\n2019年11月，全校每个楼宇至少恢复一个出水口为直饮水。\n其中的过程可以看半年前的洞。\n就这么个事儿，上一个洞主发个提倡，就被一堆人说沾点。\n很好，垃圾不用分类，轿子在你宿舍门口等着抬你。\n权益是争取来的不假，享受着权利同时还真的以为自己是RSR了，很棒。\n环保不用太多，每个人上点儿心就好。\n不上心也无所谓，大家最多也就活不到100年，后代的事儿不care很正常。", "timestamp": 1616586708, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1616658783, "url": "", "vote": {}}}